## Step 4: type-checker.ts — TypeVar Instantiation

### 4-1: registerFunctionType() — typeParams 저장 (Line 97-103)

```typescript
const fnType: Type = {
  kind: "fn",
  paramTypes,
  returnType,
  capabilities,
  typeParams: fnStmt.typeParams || [],  // Phase 5.5.4: typeParams 보존
}
```

### 4-2: checkStmt case "fn" — returnType 갱신 시 typeParams 보존 (Line 167-173)

```typescript
this.functionTypes.set(fnStmt.name, {
  kind: "fn",
  paramTypes: existingFnType.paramTypes,
  returnType: inferredReturn,
  capabilities: existingFnType.capabilities,
  typeParams: (existingFnType as any).typeParams,  // Phase 5.5.4: typeParams 보존
})
```

### 4-3: checkExpr case "call" — TypeVar Instantiation (Line 455-504)

현재 call 검증 루프 앞에 삽입:

```typescript
// Phase 5.5.4: Step 1 — 모든 arg 타입 미리 계산 (중복 호출 방지)
const argTypes: Type[] = (callExpr.args || []).map((arg: any) => this.checkExpr(arg));

// Phase 5.5.4: Step 2 — TypeVar substitution map 생성
const substitution = new Map<string, Type>();
if ((fnType.typeParams || []).length > 0) {
  for (let i = 0; i < argTypes.length; i++) {
    const paramType = fnType.paramTypes[i];
    if (paramType && paramType.kind === "typevar" && !substitution.has(paramType.name)) {
      substitution.set(paramType.name, argTypes[i]);
    }
  }
}

// 인자 타입 검사 (기존 루프 수정):
for (let i = 0; i < argTypes.length; i++) {
  const paramType = fnType.paramTypes[i] || BUILTIN_TYPES.UNKNOWN;
  const resolvedParamType = (paramType.kind === "typevar" && substitution.has(paramType.name))
    ? substitution.get(paramType.name)!
    : paramType;
  if (!typesCompatible(argTypes[i], resolvedParamType)) {
    this.addError(...);
  }
}

// Phase 5.5.4: Step 3 — returnType에 TypeVar가 있으면 substitution 적용
const retType = fnType.returnType;
if (retType.kind === "typevar" && substitution.has(retType.name)) {
  return substitution.get(retType.name)!;
}
```

